text: Maloye Baydavletovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Tazlarovsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 15 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 16 km from Isyangulovo, 6 km from Tazlarovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Maloye Baydavletovo
